152
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,360
Lu.

153
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,600
The chief said

154
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,400
if you refuse the transfer,

155
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,400
