158
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,408
Lu.

159
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,624
Lu.

160
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,320
Why interfere with my transfer?

161
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,720
