178
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,200
Lu Ye!

179
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,360
I'm over fifty and earned my position.

180
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:04,680
Using legitimate methods

181
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:07,400
to clear my child's path

182
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,680
