188
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,720
Director He,

189
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:27,520
stop these self-destructive schemes.

190
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,248
Young Master.

191
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:37,200
Sir,

192
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,760
