193
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,040
I knew it.

194
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,240
More fiery than his mother.

195
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,840
That's a good thing.

196
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,592
Go.

197
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,240
Monitor ones who approach him.

198
00:12:01,568 --> 00:12:02,080
Yes.

