Of course I am a human.

213
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:33,240
I am still alive.

214
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,400
My two brothers are gone.

215
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:38,480
So now only

216
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:41,000
I will attend to you.

217
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,160
The doctor said

218
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,920
