219
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,160
Though not caring about Ms. Tang,

220
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:50,880
you should consider your only son,

221
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,040
right?

222
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:53,920
Was it you...

223
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,800
Was it you...

224
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,600
What?

225
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,320
Are you asking
if I killed my two brothers?

226
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:09,520
They got off too easily.

227
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:11,200
I wanted to leave

228
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,440
